Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(620,670)}<Immunity>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉 人類種要完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到 到底是怎麼回事啊 誇下那種海口…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}非常抱歉 對不起 我沒有預料到舞臺是東京
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們對這裡沒轍 我們的主場其實是客場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是萬分抱歉我們排不上用場 請自己想想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這裡是主人們的世界嗎？
Comment: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你曾經很受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}非常非常受世界上的女孩子歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你過著被她們追求的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是 在你的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.82,0:00:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有一位會砰然心跳的思戀之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.31,0:00:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然而這樣的你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}面對接連不斷的誘惑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.94,0:00:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的思戀也會動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.40,0:01:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你能突破眾多的誘惑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}將愛傳達給思戀之人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an7\fs36}註：惡搞生死格鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Living Or Dead系列番外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.69,0:01:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Love Or Loved 2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}～將戀愛的子彈傳達給她～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Living Or Dead系列番外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.11,0:01:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Love Or Loved 2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:01:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}～將戀愛的子彈傳達給她～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs28\pos(240,267)}<Killing・Giant>\N{\fs40}誘導法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.88,0:02:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗷嗷～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}聽得見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}歡迎來到遊戲中的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這次就請你們在這架空場所中進行遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請讓我確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這裡是架空的場所 並不是實際存在的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是說憑你們的想像所創造的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遊戲用的假想空間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.26,0:02:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正是如此 有什麼問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別嚇我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可惡 這不讓我腦中閃過好幾次心靈創傷嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.74,0:02:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你為什麼生氣到這種地步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}我差點就要割腕自殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}別開玩笑了 老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對這個舞臺是有不滿嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}超他X的不滿！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有什麼可悲傷的非得選這種舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是精神攻擊還是找碴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.16,0:02:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最近在東部聯合的年輕人中人氣很高的SF舞臺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒什麼特別的意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}總之請放心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因為是在遊戲中 所以在某種程度是沒有關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怪不得沐浴著日光也沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白 冷靜一點 這裡不是東京
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只是很像而已 這是憑藉他們的想像製作的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.77,0:03:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒錯 這裡是在遊戲之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs36\an7}註：女神異聞錄 命運石之門 秋葉原之旅\N　　從左到右依次 卡蒂・萊科寧 牧瀨紅莉栖 里中千枝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}女O異聞錄 命O石之門 秋O原之旅之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果是在遊戲之中的話就沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遊戲之中？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的 已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就讓我來說明規則吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}首先請看腳下的箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請各位用那把槍射擊靠近過來的NPC
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 要射啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}時而射擊 時而爆破
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}讓她們對你神魂顛倒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是Gal☆Gun啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an7\fs36}註：GalGun少女射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被迷倒的女孩子會將愛的力量託付給各位然後消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}從迷戀之槍所射出的是Love Power
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是各位的愛情力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這槍的名字叫迷戀之槍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真俗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一方面 各位中的某位被伊綱射中後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.15,0:04:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就會成為伊綱的愛之奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\blur2\an7}畫面字：伊綱碳 LOVE——♥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這叫倒戈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全世界的女孩子都對自己笑臉相迎 在這之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有思戀之人對你漠然置之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}傳達這份愛的力量讓她對你神魂顛倒就是這個遊戲的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}以上 來自說明書
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是說從一開始就得甩開女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你以為你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是說伊綱讓四個人迷上自己 目標是後宮結局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們的目標只是伊綱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最後一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們所在的假想空間無法使用魔法 請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼樣 還需要更詳細說明規則嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 我們邊玩邊確認
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就先來試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}每射一擊迷戀之槍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就會消耗Love Power
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}通過擊破NPC 可以恢復Love Power
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}這是做什麼 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}太令人不快了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被NPC接觸 Love Power就會減少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Love Power消耗殆盡後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}NPC就會不再靠過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咦 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\move(640,666,640,710,660,1060)}但是 沒有了射出迷戀之槍的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就會變成事實上的無法戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼 射擊同伴會怎麼樣 老爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可以恢復Love Power的耗盡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且 可以救出被伊綱射中變成愛之奴隸的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 會一時變成射擊之人的愛之奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊啊 主人!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的妹妹喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在離我這麼近的地方竟然存在如此可愛且可人的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真想把至今都沒有注意到你的 我的雙眼挖出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 哥不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們是兄妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吉普莉爾 喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這就是在主人的書籍裡的三角關係和NTR嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就連不擁有戀愛感情的我都有點感興趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吉普莉爾 一會要調教妳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}請原諒我吧 白大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}我是按捺不住興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原來如此 在愛之奴隸的狀態的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}機能會完全停止以至於不能控制自己嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}找到你們了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們又一起放置我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}空 我的王子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\move(640,666,640,710,390,790)}史蒂芙 妳理解至今為止的規則了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的 規則什麼的都沒有必要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就算不知道那種東西 我們的愛也是永遠的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 理所當然沒有明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就把這個像這樣 這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真令人激動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然後扳動食指
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哦？ 我到底在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是多麼美妙的我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果然打到障礙物會反彈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這個彈跳性能是關鍵 白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還有雖然是在遊戲中 但是體力和現實中沒有太大區別
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儘可能地減少奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}兩位我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Comment: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}我不會鬆手的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}我要和你一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}只要有了我就什麼都不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}啊 我 watakushi我～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}嗷嗷～
Comment: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}總算是遊戲正式開始了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼樣 菲 看得見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 看得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}克拉米的視野接收得很清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(410,670)}<WereBeast>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對獸人種來說這種魔法真是不能忍受的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 維持這個術式是很困難的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是為了克拉米 我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(380,670)}<WereBeast>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}獸人種 其身體能力據說能接近物理極限
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}面對這種不得了的種族你要怎麼戰鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就讓我好好見識一下吧 空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}話說 伊綱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你最後一次感覺遊戲有趣的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果然如此嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這個才是這個遊戲的精髓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:08:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼 能做到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}目標 NPC
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}假定是棉內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}布的厚度最大為1釐米
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}十二點方向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}距離 20050
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}射入角 93
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}彈速 300m/s
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可允許擊中誤差 0.5公分以下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是我做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}開火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}失敗了！為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼樣都好了 這個笨蛋種族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你到底在高興什麼 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}輸了的話就會有很多人變得不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以必須要贏 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是贏了的話 對方會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太好了 胸罩破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就知道會是手捂胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼可能會感覺到有趣呢 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這個腳步聲是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是白 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}往這邊來了 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白 拿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒打中 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不可能 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.66,0:10:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伊綱碳應該正在大吃一驚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在集合了世界上核心槍手的FPS類遊戲中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}創造了無法動搖的記錄的並不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而是白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}運用惡魔般的計算能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}掌握敵人的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}從這之中匯出的行動模式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}算進了可能射擊的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}接近預知未來的提前射擊和回避動作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就像是射出的子彈在避開一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白的子彈就像追蹤著你打過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這太扯了 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只能逃了 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.29,0:12:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(640,670)}<Flügel>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天翼種
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是吉普莉爾 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}混淆視線的炸彈 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原來是無法飛行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吉普莉爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}躲不掉 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:12:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請讓我在你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}衣服可以當盾用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}菲 剛才的看見了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 用克拉米的眼睛看得清清楚楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白壓倒性的射擊雖然很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 沒想到空在遠方靜靜埋伏的射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她竟然在開槍前就察覺到並進行回避
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(605,670)}<WereBeast>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這就是獸人種的第六感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別瞎說了 能做到這個的話就不是第六感了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而是預知未來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出千 也就是耍賴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是作弊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原來如此 無法證明的作弊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}說成是第六感就無從反駁了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果然他們通曉這個遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比我們還懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伊綱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他們在下面的通道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白累得動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}趁現在攻下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不用你說 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}無論用什麼耍小聰明的戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他們都不可能有勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}終於輪到我們開展防衛戰的時候了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拜託了白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第一手既然沒有決出勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.23,0:14:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}從現在開始就要隨機應變
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}隨機應變？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:15:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}面對熟知遊戲的作弊對手用純粹的比試來對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在這裡遇上 你們死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為了以前的怨恨和伊綱大人 空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吉普莉爾壞壞 大家丟下我去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不會放手了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把這傢伙帶來太失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在笑 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}剛才開始這心臟也好煩 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最後感到遊戲很有趣是什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好開心 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白大人 下一個戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吉普莉爾好煩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主人 果然是太亂來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:15:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就算是白大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:15:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在遊戲中我做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白就能做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不論什麼時候都是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}從今以後也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥 相信白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊？哥哥有懷疑過妳嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這次…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就輪到哥了 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白大人為了保護主人而採取的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 我能理解所以別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白不是沒得出答案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那本身就是答案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(680,670)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是『　　』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是我們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.82,0:17:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}連白會成為敵人也包含在內的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(590,670)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}『　　』的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}剩下的我要完成我們所約定的能引導我們走向勝利的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如同魔法般的公式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是這麼回事吧 白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吉普莉爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妳去當伊綱的對手幫我爭取一點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣雖說是沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就算把她打倒也沒關係吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs36\blur2}註：出自Fate/Stay night英靈衛宮的臺詞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是這個意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我還是先吐槽一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妳這常被看作是死亡Flag
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.54,0:17:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}居然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:18:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼我就普通地打倒她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.36,0:18:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}省得我去找人的工夫了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跑去哪裡了 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你好啊 小狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有種既視感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我之前挑戰東部聯合然後失敗時的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}難不成是妳嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然主人叫我爭取時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過機會難得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好好享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}竭盡一切作弊手段
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}直到氣消為止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請再次給我添上失敗的羞恥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可惡 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這不是場所的差異就能解決的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要我怎麼辦啊 白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就這樣逃到屋頂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.23,0:19:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 這點也會被預料到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不管哪條路都會馬上被追上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等等 不覺得有點怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白為什麼不跑著追上來？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果用跑著的話 幹掉我的時機要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}盡可能地減少奔跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}說起來這麼說的不是我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果會錯了意就不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了白 哥差不多到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒有這麼對待家裡蹲的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}事到如今哥是不可能在這裡出錯的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果有你沒有想到的事的話 那就是——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我沒有想要回避 沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥 最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥也最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伊綱 就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是讓我費了好大的工夫啊 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你保存體力不去奔跑就是為了這個吧 白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥 最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不可能 剛被空打到之後應該還不能立刻自由行動才對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}內褲沒有了 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}難道說！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的只瞄準內褲開槍的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}終於注意到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白從一開始就從未變成過你們的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}打中的是衣服 然後偽裝中彈 desu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被算計了 但不過如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.41,0:22:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最後一次覺得玩遊戲很有趣是什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.89,0:22:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有趣 desu
Comment: 0,0:22:12.89,0:22:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:23:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs36\blur2}註：出自最終幻想4
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:23:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(830,670)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:23:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還差一把勁了 把力量給『　　』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.65,0:23:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}當然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.88,0:23:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs28\blur2\pos(1057,532)}<Rule‧Number‧10>\N{\fs40}收束法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:51.82,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,ベイビーベイベー  LOVE ME DO!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:54.68,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,愛の囁くよりも速く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:59.57,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,ぎゅっとその引き金を引いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:02.79,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,ベイビーベイベー　DYNAMITE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:05.50,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,理性ごと吹っ飛ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.78,0:01:11.10,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,あなた以外もう何もいらないくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:15.46,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,愛の強さ教えて欲しいの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:16.90,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,できるでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:19.48,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,解き放て弾けるパッション
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.62,0:01:25.26,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,ほらめっちゃくちゃメロメロにして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:26.43,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,愛はドッキュン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:27.88,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,恋はズッキュン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.88,0:01:29.98,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,らぶパワー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.25,0:01:33.33,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,このハートど真ん中命中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:36.28,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,いやよ…だけど　ねぇもう１回
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:37.54,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,愛はド級
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:38.83,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,恋は直球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:40.91,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,らぶモーション
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:44.36,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,カラダ中痺れちゃう want you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:48.65,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,強く撃ち抜いてくださいダーリン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:52.57,OPJP-J,,0,0,0,,お願い☆すにゃいぱー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:51.82,OPCHT,,0,0,0,,寶貝寶貝 愛我吧!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:54.68,OPCHT,,0,0,0,,比愛之細語還要快速
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:59.57,OPCHT,,0,0,0,,緊緊地扣動你的扳機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:02.79,OPCHT,,0,0,0,,寶貝寶貝 炸裂開!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:05.50,OPCHT,,0,0,0,,連同理性一起吹飛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.78,0:01:11.10,OPCHT,,0,0,0,,除你之外我再無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:15.46,OPCHT,,0,0,0,,想要讓你告訴我愛的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:16.90,OPCHT,,0,0,0,,能做到的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:19.48,OPCHT,,0,0,0,,噴射而出炸裂開來的激情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.62,0:01:25.26,OPCHT,,0,0,0,,來吧 把我迷得神魂顛倒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:26.43,OPCHT,,0,0,0,,愛情是心動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:27.88,OPCHT,,0,0,0,,戀愛是心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.88,0:01:29.98,OPCHT,,0,0,0,,愛的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.25,0:01:33.33,OPCHT,,0,0,0,,命中我心臟的正中央
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:36.28,OPCHT,,0,0,0,,不要唷…但是 吶再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:37.54,OPCHT,,0,0,0,,愛情是頂級
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:38.83,OPCHT,,0,0,0,,戀愛是直球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:40.91,OPCHT,,0,0,0,,愛的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:44.36,OPCHT,,0,0,0,,身體興奮得想要你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:48.65,OPCHT,,0,0,0,,親愛的請用力射穿我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:52.57,OPCHT,,0,0,0,,拜託了☆射手喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.23,0:22:45.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}誰にも言えない孤独を抱えたまま一人で泣いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.70,0:22:57.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}誰にも上手に笑えない僕ら二人出会って笑った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:23:04.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}真夜中すぎに　想像の奥に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}どうしようもない気持ちをただ押しやって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:14.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}サヨナラ　僕らはきっと生まれ変われるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:18.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}悲しみに手を振るんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:25.79,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}そしていつか空っぽのままの心に灯りをともすように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:32.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}とぎれとぎれの　言葉を探して繋ぎ止めた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:38.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}それでもたった二人の世界は続いてくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.05,0:23:46.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}空に祈るように　どうか永遠に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.23,0:22:45.70,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}將無法對別人說出口的孤獨藏於心中 一個人哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.70,0:22:57.66,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}無法對別人好好笑出來的我們 相遇了歡笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:23:04.00,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}在午夜過後之時 在想像深處之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.03,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}只是將無可奈何的心情拋在一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:14.90,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}再見了 因為我們一定能夠重獲新生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:18.98,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}對悲傷揮揮手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:25.79,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}然後曾經空蕩蕩的心靈就會像點燃了明燈一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:32.18,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}尋找斷斷續續的話語 將它們系在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:38.05,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}儘管如此兩人的世界還是會繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.05,0:23:46.76,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}像天空祈禱 請一定要相伴永遠
